  * doc/Makefile: Build HTML manpages for the Vietnamese translation.
  * doc/po4a/po/ru.po: Updated translation. Thanks to Sergey Alyoshin.
  * doc/po4a/po/fr.po: Likewise. Thanks to Florentin Duneau.

